{"questionId": "8f775d79-fed4-4c35-a5f2-19a8f62db4bb_4", "correctAnswer": "D", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Solve the system by elimination", "content": "Add the equations: $3y+(-3y)=(8x+18)+(7x-26)$, so $0=15x-8$, giving $x=\\tfrac{8}{15}$."}, {"title": "Find $30x$", "content": "Multiply: $30x=30\\cdot\\tfrac{8}{15}=16$. That matches choice <strong>D</strong> — <strong>D</strong> is correct."}]}